asset_contract.name: Rabbit College Club
asset_contract.description:
Rabbit College Club is an NFT collection of 10,000 rabbits. Each rabbit is also your ticket to College Club, a social platform for members. Ownership includes your rabbit's creative and commercial rights.

The entire amount raised from the first month of secondary sales on OpenSea will be donated to charity in support of the idea of no animal testing.

https://discord.gg/f5rvq3F57p
